Project: BooxStream
Repository: https://github.com/piyushdaiya/booxstream

BooxStream is an open-source Android screen streaming and host
client tool designed for Boox devices and Android-based e-ink systems.
It provides a streaming pipeline using Android MediaProjection,
VP8 encoding, and a host-side client.

Additional notices or third-party attributions may be added here
